{"id":119932,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/《人民日报》在911创造了自己独特的历史/","date":"2010-11-06T01:15:11Z","modified":"2010-11-06T01:15:11Z","title":"《人民日报》在911创造了自己独特的历史","content":"<p><span>今天围观了美国新闻博物馆，这是一个民间机构。里面内容非常丰富，把美国媒体发展史上重要的人和事和文献都陈列出来了。</span><wbr><br />\n<br /><span>其中有一个角落是911时期的新闻。这里有一面墙，在这面墙上，人民日报以其特有的方式，创造了自己的历史。先看下面这段话的倒数第二句－－</span><wbr><br />\n<br /><wbr><a href=\"http://b55.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59a7437f15c5738d6ff8dda7220068a9235c9870a3ee2600ab14bdd8ed979f8f68c50d39d805e7cb7b1f547e2f5e42e0ac34b12d1eda610ace78d9b79a80c6965314148ed6&#038;a=55&#038;b=55\"><img src=\"http://b55.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59a7437f15c5738d6ff8dda7220068a9235c9870a3ee2600ab14bdd8ed979f8f68c50d39d805e7cb7b1f547e2f5e42e0ac34b12d1eda610ace78d9b79a80c6965314148ed6&#038;a=55&#038;b=55\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;><br />\n<br /><span><wbr><span><span><wbr>自由媒体是民主的基石</span><wbr></span><wbr><br />\n<br /></span><wbr><span>人民有知道真相的需求，记者有说话的权利</span><wbr><br />\n<br /><span>发掘真相可能很困难，报道故事或许很危险</span><wbr><br />\n<br /><span>自由包括不入主流的权利，责任包括维护公正的义务</span><wbr><br />\n<br /><span>新闻是正在书写的历史，记者提供历史的初稿</span><wbr><br />\n<br /><span>自由媒体的最高境界，是揭示真相</span><wbr></p>\n<p><span>“新闻是正在书写的历史”－－2001.9.11，人民日报这份媒体，书写了独属于它的历史。</span><wbr><br />\n<br /><span>下面是新闻博物馆陈列的911事件发生后，美国国内和其他34个国家共127份主要媒体的头条</span><wbr>。<br />\n<br /><wbr><a href=\"http://b48.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd597a1c65a05fd229414efd33975d23f3aa8efcf00b7f5cde72dbf89485ebb54a1f583f496a1f0b183c101f1921184213f409f436ebad155e44348f617a1bab343aefc56754&#038;a=55&#038;b=48\"><img src=\"http://b48.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd597a1c65a05fd229414efd33975d23f3aa8efcf00b7f5cde72dbf89485ebb54a1f583f496a1f0b183c101f1921184213f409f436ebad155e44348f617a1bab343aefc56754&#038;a=55&#038;b=48\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;></p>\n<p><wbr><a href=\"http://b53.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59bdd3d0a77f52844e0b9cd3a980a5cf3a2069fc2339e0def93247ac18198bfd2026d5136048c701b7a21bd40f6ee0072b3c2cb4a57630e0e21db3ffc293e7646ddc4651fb&#038;a=56&#038;b=53\"><img src=\"http://b53.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59bdd3d0a77f52844e0b9cd3a980a5cf3a2069fc2339e0def93247ac18198bfd2026d5136048c701b7a21bd40f6ee0072b3c2cb4a57630e0e21db3ffc293e7646ddc4651fb&#038;a=56&#038;b=53\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;></p>\n<p><wbr><a href=\"http://b53.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd594d99384564ea106bbb712de186b2fc1484f152f78b451b7fa1cbca27b089aa9e5fd810b6ec4b740368d04f73f3a2978b4045c5874a04cfeea3b5b8a192131737752f216e&#038;a=53&#038;b=53\"><img src=\"http://b53.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd594d99384564ea106bbb712de186b2fc1484f152f78b451b7fa1cbca27b089aa9e5fd810b6ec4b740368d04f73f3a2978b4045c5874a04cfeea3b5b8a192131737752f216e&#038;a=53&#038;b=53\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;></p>\n<p><wbr><a href=\"http://b59.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59055682e805c500819b8655e1203240466e6df5b4e3b74e8944243d83f72520c74eada4ecbdf34dd2e8bc7c2bd24ccb0e6a5dcd2ab960847a6db7b5e9f52e215842d3af13&#038;a=18&#038;b=59\"><img src=\"http://b59.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59055682e805c500819b8655e1203240466e6df5b4e3b74e8944243d83f72520c74eada4ecbdf34dd2e8bc7c2bd24ccb0e6a5dcd2ab960847a6db7b5e9f52e215842d3af13&#038;a=18&#038;b=59\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;></p>\n<p><wbr><a href=\"http://b18.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd5930f8fa4531cf6ecc227316e0ef57e897a5830f77f87c863b659f4c269e8e88739b1a0d4bcad716d07de8b4a21b7ded8992ecf781360d41db039f71c301d42433d8869c78&#038;a=53&#038;b=18\"><img src=\"http://b18.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd5930f8fa4531cf6ecc227316e0ef57e897a5830f77f87c863b659f4c269e8e88739b1a0d4bcad716d07de8b4a21b7ded8992ecf781360d41db039f71c301d42433d8869c78&#038;a=53&#038;b=18\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;></p>\n<p><wbr><a href=\"http://b18.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59f8aabe2c3c04e906fd9831ef30c6aa6da9d83b7cb15d915939b41bc47c2cd430e0b1ca8ce47252b10c559e89d3bf845db80d697752403fff164a9dd93adea94fca4b1618&#038;a=55&#038;b=18\"><img src=\"http://b18.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59f8aabe2c3c04e906fd9831ef30c6aa6da9d83b7cb15d915939b41bc47c2cd430e0b1ca8ce47252b10c559e89d3bf845db80d697752403fff164a9dd93adea94fca4b1618&#038;a=55&#038;b=18\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;></p>\n<p><wbr><a href=\"http://b56.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59c44c261f4c3a1b8d67fc0726a3253650488ef94f6023fde793d17565f25b7ebd3aec145369e32af30f62624b7ae28ea3d9b51ff9c55e40e72c30bc7c4a49080c97a475d1&#038;a=59&#038;b=56\"><img src=\"http://b56.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59c44c261f4c3a1b8d67fc0726a3253650488ef94f6023fde793d17565f25b7ebd3aec145369e32af30f62624b7ae28ea3d9b51ff9c55e40e72c30bc7c4a49080c97a475d1&#038;a=59&#038;b=56\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;></p>\n<p><wbr><a href=\"http://b56.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59348c8d08e5143132ef432211ca8672486554a72329dc5f90fa35e335760eff940b304d3c41bc511c2e634adf074024f0a4c813f2ece7f24fddd932c0479fac8115999738&#038;a=48&#038;b=56\"><img src=\"http://b56.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59348c8d08e5143132ef432211ca8672486554a72329dc5f90fa35e335760eff940b304d3c41bc511c2e634adf074024f0a4c813f2ece7f24fddd932c0479fac8115999738&#038;a=48&#038;b=56\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;></p>\n<p><span>左上角有份报纸显得与众不同，仔细一看，原来是《人民日报》，头条竟然是“九运会火炬传递点起跑仪式举行”！－－</span><wbr><br />\n<br /><wbr><a href=\"http://b56.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59e84ff6f33352288845e994aef6b6bbb99a424272de110997eb3e77bb07268097e0db3cfa50bd48b5d3f319d258ca7479de9df005d09918a6a25f7da5cc006dc4cfcaaac9&#038;a=53&#038;b=56\"><img src=\"http://b56.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59e84ff6f33352288845e994aef6b6bbb99a424272de110997eb3e77bb07268097e0db3cfa50bd48b5d3f319d258ca7479de9df005d09918a6a25f7da5cc006dc4cfcaaac9&#038;a=53&#038;b=56\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;></p>\n<p><span>这一天，人民日报创造了独属于它自己的历史，使自己在新闻史和新闻博物馆里永久性地占有了一席之地。从下图里，你能找到独特的《人民日报》吗？</span><wbr></p>\n<p><wbr><a href=\"http://b54.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd597be5ed94bcc75fc7fcf1509be7bfe8e2c7e46b9093a81aae512621f1d9841b2b0d019f50724ffc2cc71476a5f9cbed54787a86718e8275a59166e5e0dbe10d5f0508536e&#038;a=54&#038;b=54\"><img src=\"http://b54.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd597be5ed94bcc75fc7fcf1509be7bfe8e2c7e46b9093a81aae512621f1d9841b2b0d019f50724ffc2cc71476a5f9cbed54787a86718e8275a59166e5e0dbe10d5f0508536e&#038;a=54&#038;b=54\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;></p>\n<p><wbr><a href=\"http://b55.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59f8397f52fc55bd1449e3f6961c7615dc043f487fe08c9f20dda75ce7fff781a7b07b3b67020806d979573a0895935ac4e1b47154035926fe0aa48637a9790bf8349ba591&#038;a=18&#038;b=55\"><img src=\"http://b55.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59f8397f52fc55bd1449e3f6961c7615dc043f487fe08c9f20dda75ce7fff781a7b07b3b67020806d979573a0895935ac4e1b47154035926fe0aa48637a9790bf8349ba591&#038;a=18&#038;b=55\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;><br />\n<br /><span>上面这个扭曲的铁架，来自世贸中心顶尖的一段－－</span><wbr><br />\n<br /><wbr><a href=\"http://b56.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59716eb610e3e3c5ea42a58fc019a93c482bde74d07cb7af312f09e766e8ec6ff8a1837639ac22ba05217dad10f1ef553e220312c7fbbdda37d1621ee251d6423a59f6a066&#038;a=59&#038;b=56\"><img src=\"http://b56.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59716eb610e3e3c5ea42a58fc019a93c482bde74d07cb7af312f09e766e8ec6ff8a1837639ac22ba05217dad10f1ef553e220312c7fbbdda37d1621ee251d6423a59f6a066&#038;a=59&#038;b=56\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;><br />\n<br /><wbr><a href=\"http://b59.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59af6a527de7f91d97eea783abb01feaaf0681a567b2e199fc772969a304058a074cb572058c7f7be5e6b4556cafa195471b0f3f3c560389e438e9b381c0868c141d687286&#038;a=59&#038;b=59\"><img src=\"http://b59.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59af6a527de7f91d97eea783abb01feaaf0681a567b2e199fc772969a304058a074cb572058c7f7be5e6b4556cafa195471b0f3f3c560389e438e9b381c0868c141d687286&#038;a=59&#038;b=59\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;><br />\n<br /><span>让人民知道真相，国家将变得安全（问题是领导将不再安全）</span><wbr></p>\n<p><span>PS.其他</span><wbr></p>\n<p>　　&#8211;><wbr><a href=\"http://b59.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59f6ea6591cd30fd96c783b1c55a59c1bf75b915886144a21ad9a0ab8ae25b8697d9fae768060254dcdd87924f0c3cf6e9c4d46bdb30a30f0dea1092949e7d569a2c759748&#038;a=48&#038;b=59\"><img src=\"http://b59.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59f6ea6591cd30fd96c783b1c55a59c1bf75b915886144a21ad9a0ab8ae25b8697d9fae768060254dcdd87924f0c3cf6e9c4d46bdb30a30f0dea1092949e7d569a2c759748&#038;a=48&#038;b=59\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;><br />\n<br />这是柏林墙实物。<br />\n<br /><wbr><a href=\"http://b53.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59d339841af844277650bb5b8b899c4510ac007fdae0fb2fbb44a3b26e79f4c1c836da8e29f33f2400de31f113090fbf375d4af6b9b495a20ddd78748556bf1dbfa195cd4a&#038;a=56&#038;b=53\"><img src=\"http://b53.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59d339841af844277650bb5b8b899c4510ac007fdae0fb2fbb44a3b26e79f4c1c836da8e29f33f2400de31f113090fbf375d4af6b9b495a20ddd78748556bf1dbfa195cd4a&#038;a=56&#038;b=53\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;><br />\n<br /><span>行动起来！</span><wbr><br />\n<br /><wbr><a href=\"http://b55.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59e076a38f534cd23611ffa4c534ec7d2a09f5a27149401c0da8ca5c1bba9de91f7ce1f085910867d0befaf60974770463f21209ae7bb169d02a52169aba472df08ae67281&#038;a=59&#038;b=55\"><img src=\"http://b55.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59e076a38f534cd23611ffa4c534ec7d2a09f5a27149401c0da8ca5c1bba9de91f7ce1f085910867d0befaf60974770463f21209ae7bb169d02a52169aba472df08ae67281&#038;a=59&#038;b=55\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;><br />\n<br />柏林墙后东德一侧的岗楼。<br />\n<br /><a href=\"http://user.kdnet.net/\">2可器</a><wbr> 于 2010-11-5 12:35:45 跟贴回复：<br />\n<br />&#8211;><wbr><a href=\"http://b48.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd590dce9403c932e5af8e18c75f6f2062cf73b38ba44698d5330c70945325aad189bc73d7576a2903e294f3a82cfd1d765955a1741b4fff02acbbae52a83c2eb77dff5b3563&#038;a=18&#038;b=48\"><img src=\"http://b48.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd590dce9403c932e5af8e18c75f6f2062cf73b38ba44698d5330c70945325aad189bc73d7576a2903e294f3a82cfd1d765955a1741b4fff02acbbae52a83c2eb77dff5b3563&#038;a=18&#038;b=48\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;><br />\n<br /><span>在肯尼迪中心一个米的展示中，正好有翻越柏林墙的形象化表现：</span><wbr><br />\n<br /><span>左边是1961－1985年间，因翻越柏林墙而被杀的人；右边则是翻越柏林墙的人。</span><wbr><br />\n<br />&#8211;><wbr><a href=\"http://b59.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd598b3a1846611e98c3cfa407bc2ef2e1e182887cd68c0fd0a36403c949153374a5f2fc225178c12a47acc4e294e7fcd6d06eb04c82b1a5624a0d5b732b854037d5f626965c&#038;a=56&#038;b=59\"><img src=\"http://b59.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd598b3a1846611e98c3cfa407bc2ef2e1e182887cd68c0fd0a36403c949153374a5f2fc225178c12a47acc4e294e7fcd6d06eb04c82b1a5624a0d5b732b854037d5f626965c&#038;a=56&#038;b=59\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;><br />\n<br /><span>博物馆里陈列了一个门板。这东东来自2005年新奥尔良风灾，是主人家警告欲得不轨的歹徒别想进门捞财。上面写着：</span><wbr><br />\n<br /><span>“试都别试，哥正在里面睡觉。还有一只大狗，一个暴丑的三八婆，两门短炮，一杆铁鎯头···”</span><wbr><br />\n<br /><span>这厮天灾人祸在眼前，还不忘搞笑。</span><wbr><br />\n<br />&#8211;><wbr><a href=\"http://b53.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd591f736e76a74392168d51592b9dba95b33630f03cd98b07dc7119ec4ed24adf4eff2bfa552dc1789d6056e1223c29dbb23abd73106d4be5bd213af842abcf0bcba7764f80&#038;a=59&#038;b=53\"><img src=\"http://b53.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd591f736e76a74392168d51592b9dba95b33630f03cd98b07dc7119ec4ed24adf4eff2bfa552dc1789d6056e1223c29dbb23abd73106d4be5bd213af842abcf0bcba7764f80&#038;a=59&#038;b=53\" /></a><wbr>500)this.width=500;&#8221;><br />\n<br /><span>这个叉是新奥儿良风灾时救灾人员在现场留下的符号。上面是时期：表示9月9日来搜求过；左边是</span><wbr><br />\n<br /><span>搜救队番号；下面是发现的人数，ODB意为没发现尸体；右边是关于水电气的提示。</span><wbr></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[9807]}